## Retest checklist (production WhatsApp)

1. Hindi filter tap → Hindi buttons + Hindi filter result text.
2. Booked visit + price question → no Book Visit button.
3. Sold unit by name → clear sold message + View Listings.
4. Hi (Hindi lead, custom template) → bilingual.
5. Hindi area query (e.g. Whitefield Devanagari) → project list matches English query.

## Safety nets

1. `npm run smoke` before deploy.
2. Deploy: `RAILWAY_ACCOUNT_TOKEN=... node scripts/deploy-railway-graphql.mjs`
3. Prod health: `https://investo-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/health/live`
